OL,3,CBBC Board apologises for 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' after Tim Westwood
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe BBC Board has apologised after a
OL,8,Freview into what the broadcaster knew
OL,9,Fabout concerns over former Radio 1 DJ
OL,10,FTim Westwood's conduct found it had
OL,11,F"missed opportunities that might have
OL,12,Fled to action".
OL,14,FThe publication of the report, which
OL,15,Fsaw barrister Gemma White KC
OL,16,Fcommissioned in 2022 by the BBC Board
OL,17,Fto examine what was known about
OL,18,FWestwood's alleged conduct during his
OL,19,Ftime at the corporation, has been
OL,20,Fdelayed at various points.
