OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FIn December the BBC paused its
OL,8,Fpublication of the report at the
OL,9,Frequest of the Metropolitan Police.
OL,11,FWestwood, who stepped down from his
OL,12,Fshow on Capital Xtra in April 2022,
OL,13,Fand left Radio 1 and Radio 1Xtra in
OL,14,F2013 after nearly 20 years, faces
OL,15,Fhistorical sexual abuse allegations
OL,16,Ffrom multiple women, and "strongly
OL,17,Fdenies all allegations of
OL,18,Finappropriate behaviour".
OL,26,@xD@ZOUzD@XO]
