OL,3,CBBC Board apologises for 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' after Tim Westwood
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"It is clear, however, that there were
OL,8,Finstances where the organisation
OL,9,Fmissed opportunities that might have
OL,10,Fled to action. Allegations were
OL,11,Ftreated in isolation rather than being
OL,12,Fbrought together. Had this happened,
OL,13,Fthe BBC may have seen a pattern of
OL,14,Fbehaviour that it could have acted on.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
