OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F406A1740745373
OL,3,CBBC Board apologises for 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' after Tim Westwood
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"Beyond assessing any alleged
OL,8,Fcriminality, which is a matter for the
OL,9,Fpolice, it is clear there were times
OL,10,Fwhere the BBC, on learning about
OL,11,Fconcerns regarding Mr Westwood's
OL,12,Fbehaviour, did not take adequate
OL,13,Faction.
OL,15,F"There is evidence of bullying and
OL,16,Fmisogynistic behaviour on the part of
OL,17,FMr Westwood and the plain fact is that
OL,18,Fhis general conduct was entirely
OL,19,Fincompatible with BBC values ` not
OL,20,Fjust now, but then.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
