OL,3,CBBC Board apologises for 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' after Tim Westwood
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"The organisation fell short and
OL,8,Ffailed people ` including our own
OL,9,Fstaff ` who had a right to expect
OL,10,Fbetter from us."
OL,12,FThe BBC Board further said they "take
OL,13,Fthis opportunity to apologise on
OL,14,Fbehalf of the entire BBC to anyone
OL,15,Fimpacted by what the review has found.
OL,16,FYour voice has been heard, and the
OL,17,Ffindings of the review will further
OL,18,Ffuel the drive to ensure it does not
OL,19,Fhappen again".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@PO]tD@aOU{D@MO]
