OL,7,FThe cost of the review is
OL,8,Fapproximately #3.3 million, the BBC
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FIn her findings, the report's author
OL,12,FMs White said: "I have not found there
OL,13,Fto be significant BBC knowledge of
OL,14,Fallegations or concerns about sexual
OL,15,Fmisconduct on Tim Westwood's part.
OL,26,@tD@POU
