OL,3,CBBC Board apologises for 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' after Tim Westwood
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,F"However, the overview from which I
OL,8,Fhave benefited as a result of having
OL,9,Fconducted this review demonstrates the
OL,10,Fclear need for a robust mechanism for
OL,11,Fthe assessment of the risks presented
OL,12,Fby the engagement of particular
OL,13,Findividuals.
OL,15,F"There were, in my view, a range of
OL,16,Ffactors which ought to have alerted
OL,17,Fthe BBC to the possibility that Tim
OL,18,FWestwood might present a risk to young
OL,19,Fwomen and girls."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@QO]
