OL,4,Copportunities' after Tim Westwood
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FPeople who reported allegations
OL,8,Fagainst Westwood told the report's
OL,9,Fauthor they were "concerned that they
OL,10,Fwould not be believed or might be
OL,11,Fblamed" for his behaviour.
OL,13,FThe report said one person told Ms
OL,14,FWhite that "Tim Westwood was very
OL,15,Fpopular so no-one wanted to listen".
OL,17,FIt said: "A common theme amongst those
OL,18,Fwho reported allegations was that they
OL,19,Fdid not know or understand at the time
OL,20,Fthat the behaviour which they had
OL,21,Fdescribed to me was wrong.
OL,26,@qD@ROUsD@GO]vD@LOUwD@cO]yD@JOU
