OL,7,F"Some said they had only realised when
OL,8,Fthey were older, or recently.
OL,10,F"One person referred to not
OL,11,Funderstanding at the time what sexual
OL,12,Fassault was."
OL,14,FThe report also said one alleged
OL,15,Fvictim "felt they would not be taken
OL,16,Fseriously and described the conduct as
OL,17,Fbeing 'so public and brazen' that Tim
OL,18,FWestwood clearly felt comfortable
OL,19,Fdoing it".
