OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FOver the last couple of years, the BBC
OL,8,Fhas taken action, including
OL,9,Fintroducing a "new anti-bullying and
OL,10,Fharassment policy", as well as a
OL,11,F"dedicated 'support at work' team to
OL,12,Faddress bullying and harassment cases".
OL,14,FThe barrister leading the review said
OL,15,Fin the report that Westwood declined
OL,16,Fto take part but his lawyers provided
OL,17,Fa statement.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@RO]sD@AOUtD@fO]
