OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FIt said he "strongly denies that his
OL,8,Fbehaviour ever amounted to bullying or
OL,9,Fharassment", and said some people
OL,10,F"behaved poorly towards" him.
OL,12,FThe statement said he "complained to
OL,13,Fthe controller about this negative
OL,14,Fbehaviour at the time and he was
OL,15,Fessentially advised to rise above it".
OL,17,FMr Westwood also said that his
OL,18,Fdecision to move to a new time slot in
OL,19,F2009 was "political, and the
OL,20,Fproduction staff made it clear that
OL,21,Fthey did not agree with it".
