OL,7,F"The environment felt competitive and
OL,8,Fhostile," he said.
OL,10,F"It was toxic from the outset. Mr
OL,11,FWestwood worked incredibly hard on the
OL,12,Fshow and had high standards.
OL,14,F"On certain occasions, he took issue
OL,15,Fwith some of his colleagues' poor
OL,16,Fattitude to work and low productivity,
OL,17,Fand expressed his opinion that they
OL,18,Fwere lazy and out of touch with the
OL,19,Faudience.
